}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "Atmel Combo-USB AT567B1-2" is printed on the chip :(w/ AT76C505 on it in another shot). "1709-1-6142" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
It is presumed to be a ''Mitac'' module based on the MAC label :affixed to the board in the FCC photos. Used in some HP printers.
